			<div id="post-26" class="post-26 post type-post hentry category-fruits-vegetables">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.redbudfarms.com/can-fruits-vegetables-help-you-reduce-weight/" title="Permalink to Can Fruits &amp; Vegetables Help You Reduce Weight" rel="bookmark">Can Fruits &amp; Vegetables Help You Reduce Weight</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.redbudfarms.com/can-fruits-vegetables-help-you-reduce-weight/" title="10:30 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">February 9, 2011</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.redbudfarms.com/author/firstpage/" title="View all posts by Barley">Barley</a></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

				<div class="entry-content">
				<p>Most people this time are having a hard time in losing weight. They tend to buy and drink different diet tea, capsules and even having a daily exercise. Though those are helpful things to do when a person wants to loss weight, but not all can carry out or create a huge change in your weight. Well, there are a lot of helpful ways and techniques that can loss weight, but these days the most effective and healthy ways that you can take in order to loss weight are eating fresh fruits and vegetables. Do you know how can fruits and vegetables help you loss weight?</p>
<p><a href="http://www.redbudfarms.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Fresh_Fruits_and_Vegetables1.jpg"><img class="alignright size-medium wp-image-29" src="http://www.redbudfarms.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/02/Fresh_Fruits_and_Vegetables1-225x300.jpg" alt="" width="225" height="300" /></a>Experience is the finest teacher in choosing quality but here are a few pointers on buying some types of how can fruits and vegetables help us. Choose asparagus with very little white and more tender. Use asparagus soon after purchasing because it toughens rapidly. Beans or snap are the best just avoid beans with dry looking pods. Flower clusters on broccoli, Brussels sprouts and cauliflower should be tight and close together. Brussels sprouts must be firm and compact, Smudgy dirty spots may indicate insects. Cabbage and head lettuce, pick heads heavy for size, avoid cabbage with worm holes and lettuce with discoloration or soft rot. Lastly, peas and lima beans just make sure you select pods that are well-filled but not bulging. Avoid dry, spotted, yellowed, or flabby pods.</p>
<p>Select plump, solid berries with good color. Avoid stained containers indicating wet or leaky berries. Berries such as blackberries, raspberries with clinging caps might be unripe. Strawberries without caps may be too ripe. Melons and cantaloupes are ripe when the stems scar is smooth and space between the netting is yellow or yellow-green. They are best to eat when fully ripe and fruity odor. Lastly, oranges with a slight greenish tinge may be just as ripe as fully colored ones. Light or greenish-yellow lemons are tarter than deep yellow ones. Avoid citrus fruits showing withered, deep-set, or soft areas. So you already know what can fruits &amp; vegetables help you loss weight with good benefits.</p>
							</div><!-- .entry-content -->
	
